Rating: 4
This is great! It's unusual, but oh so good! I made this for a dinner party and everyone loved it. I made it ahead of time and just re-warmed it in the microwave. And the leftovers were even better the next day. I think the flavors blended more. I told my vegetarian friend about the recipe. She made it for dinner one night, and said that it was a real hit with her husband. This is a real keeper!

